Global Aircraft Wankel Engine Market Insights
Aircraft Wankel Engine Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Aircraft Wankel Engine Market Overview
The global Aircraft Wankel Engine market is valued at USD 210 million in 2024 and is projected to grow at a CAGR of 7.2% from 2024 to 2032. The increasing demand for efficient and lightweight engine solutions in aviation, especially in UAVs (Unmanned Aerial Vehicles) and small aircraft, is driving this growth. The Wankel engine’s compact design and high power-to-weight ratio make it an attractive alternative to conventional piston engines. Technological advancements and enhanced fuel efficiency are expected to further boost market demand. The market's expansion is also fueled by a shift towards hybrid and electric propulsion systems, where Wankel engines can play a pivotal role in reducing fuel consumption and emissions in aviation applications.

